 Burna Boy Award-winning Nigerian musician, Burna Boy has arrived in his home state, River State for his homecoming concert. The singer arrived at the Port Harcourt airport not long ago and he will be performing at the concert. The concert is organized by the state government and it is organized to appreciate him for his efforts on the music scene. This comes after he won the World Music Album award at the just ended Grammy Awards. Prior to the event, it was revealed that he was charging the government a whopping N100 million. View this post on Instagram A post shared by Olorisupergal (@olorisupergal)